        <h6>Brihadeeshwar Temple is one of the most beautiful architectural splendors of the country. It is erected amidst the great walls made perhaps in the sixteenth century.<a hreflang="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brihadisvara_Temple,_Thanjavur">Read more...</a></h6></div>


       
